1
00:01:09,820 --> 00:01:13,500
=Inherently Kind=

2
00:01:14,780 --> 00:01:17,620
=Episode 18=
(Falling Apart)

3
00:01:18,439 --> 00:01:18,920
Mr. He.

4
00:01:19,280 --> 00:01:20,319
Although Mr. Wang and Mr. Liang

5
00:01:20,519 --> 00:01:22,079
have been removed from the board,

6
00:01:22,640 --> 00:01:24,000
Mu Shaoze and Su Li

7
00:01:24,319 --> 00:01:25,159
have also completely fallen out.

8
00:01:25,519 --> 00:01:27,359
Everything is going
according to your plan.

9
00:01:29,560 --> 00:01:32,719
Mu Shaoze is nothing but
a ruthless businessman.

10
00:01:33,439 --> 00:01:35,840
Profit always comes before women.

11
00:01:38,159 --> 00:01:38,959
So that is it.

12
00:01:39,760 --> 00:01:41,840
Why would he suddenly go after

13
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:42,799
a married woman?

14
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:44,000
Turns out

15
00:01:44,760 --> 00:01:47,519
he was after Gu Corporation all along.

16
00:01:48,239 --> 00:01:50,200
So what do we do next?

17
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:54,400
Drive the resort into
complete bankruptcy

18
00:01:55,519 --> 00:01:56,599
and buy it at rock-bottom price.

19
00:01:58,480 --> 00:02:00,239
Shaoze has been so good to me.

20
00:02:00,799 --> 00:02:01,439
Good.

21
00:02:01,640 --> 00:02:02,760
That puts my mind at ease.

22
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:05,640
Qingmei.

23
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:07,359
You are back.

24
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:08,960
Dad.

25
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:12,639
Jinxi has good news to share.

26
00:02:13,759 --> 00:02:14,400
Qingmei,

27
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:17,080
Shaoze and I are getting engaged.

28
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,039
Congratulations.

29
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:21,080
You are a perfect match.

30
00:02:24,639 --> 00:02:25,360
Shaoze said

31
00:02:25,599 --> 00:02:27,639
you have stepped down as
Chairman of Gu Corporation.

32
00:02:27,919 --> 00:02:28,560
That is for the best.

33
00:02:28,919 --> 00:02:30,199
I've always been worried about
you overworking.

34
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:31,960
Now you can finally rest.

35
00:02:32,719 --> 00:02:33,639
I'm pretty tired.

36
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:34,919
I'll go upstairs and rest now.

37
00:02:36,599 --> 00:02:37,319
I'll leave you to your chat.

38
00:02:43,159 --> 00:02:43,639
Dad,

39
00:02:44,159 --> 00:02:46,120
when do you think we should set

40
00:02:46,199 --> 00:02:47,159
our engagement date?

41
00:02:48,719 --> 00:02:49,840
I have already consulted someone.

42
00:02:50,319 --> 00:02:51,159
It's on the 8th of next month.

43
00:02:51,639 --> 00:02:52,520
The 8th of next month?

44
00:02:52,639 --> 00:02:53,280
Perfect.

45
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:55,039
Then I'll follow your arrangement.

46
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:57,800
Shaoze,

47
00:02:58,639 --> 00:03:00,520
Jinxi is the princess of our family.

48
00:03:00,879 --> 00:03:02,479
Don't bully her.

49
00:03:04,479 --> 00:03:05,240
Why would I?

50
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:07,759
As long as she doesn't bully me.

51
00:03:10,039 --> 00:03:10,719
Shaoze,

52
00:03:11,439 --> 00:03:13,439
Your father would be so happy

53
00:03:14,599 --> 00:03:15,599
to see you two engaged.

54
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:17,879
Yes.

55
00:03:18,919 --> 00:03:20,840
Unfortunately,
my father has passed away,

56
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:23,319
and my mother is too ill

57
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:24,960
to return from abroad.

58
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:28,520
On that day,

59
00:03:28,879 --> 00:03:31,360
we'll need you for everything, Uncle He.

60
00:03:37,599 --> 00:03:38,439
Alright.

61
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:39,479
Got it.

62
00:03:40,439 --> 00:03:42,400
The payment process is out of my hands.

63
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:45,919
Mr. Tang,

64
00:03:46,599 --> 00:03:47,639
your business is doing so well.

65
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,120
Not at all.

66
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:51,840
You are not leaving today.

67
00:03:53,080 --> 00:03:53,759
Drink with me.

68
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:56,479
Finish this shot first.

69
00:03:58,879 --> 00:03:59,479
Boss,

70
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:00,000
I...

71
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:01,120
I have some business to do.

72
00:04:03,199 --> 00:04:03,840
Our people

73
00:04:04,039 --> 00:04:05,719
have spotted Gu Qingmei abroad.

74
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:07,159
But she is on high alert

75
00:04:07,240 --> 00:04:08,039
and has gone to ground.

76
00:04:08,159 --> 00:04:09,960
We have not found
her exact location yet.

77
00:04:13,639 --> 00:04:14,800
Then confirm it as soon as possible.

78
00:04:15,120 --> 00:04:15,560
Yes.

79
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:18,319
Are we done with business?

80
00:04:21,879 --> 00:04:22,399
Boss,

81
00:04:22,639 --> 00:04:23,560
you are still young.

82
00:04:23,879 --> 00:04:25,240
You need to take care of yourself.

83
00:04:26,079 --> 00:04:26,639
Besides,

84
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:27,759
you are not even married.

85
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:28,279
You...

86
00:04:28,399 --> 00:04:29,839
You just want to bring that up,
don't you?

87
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:33,040
Get out!

88
00:04:46,639 --> 00:04:47,279
Everyone,

89
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:48,920
the situation is very clear.

90
00:04:49,160 --> 00:04:50,360
The truth is right there.

91
00:04:51,160 --> 00:04:53,839
Gu Corporation's resort
profited from customers' privacy

92
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:56,040
- and is stalling with an investigation.
- Miss Lin.

93
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:58,639
They clearly have no intention
of giving me justice!

94
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:00,120
A business like this

95
00:05:00,279 --> 00:05:01,800
should be shut down immediately.

96
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:02,680
- Am I right?
- Miss Lin,

97
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:03,319
please calm down.

98
00:05:03,439 --> 00:05:04,560
We are working on it.

99
00:05:04,879 --> 00:05:05,560
Shut up!

100
00:05:06,879 --> 00:05:08,000
You are also an employee here,

101
00:05:08,199 --> 00:05:09,879
no different from them.

102
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:11,040
I know.

103
00:05:11,639 --> 00:05:13,519
You just want me to keep quiet,

104
00:05:13,759 --> 00:05:14,240
don't you?

105
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:15,399
Let me tell you.

106
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:16,560
I don't want any compensation.

107
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:18,639
I only want the public to see the truth.

108
00:05:18,839 --> 00:05:19,480
The truth...

109
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:21,240
- Madam Gu.
- We demand the truth!

110
00:05:23,079 --> 00:05:23,720
Get her wound treated.

111
00:05:23,839 --> 00:05:24,279
Alright.

112
00:05:24,879 --> 00:05:25,279
This way.

113
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:27,600
Don't waste time here.

114
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:28,639
If I don't get

115
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:29,600
a satisfactory answer today,

116
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:31,800
my followers will come here

117
00:05:32,199 --> 00:05:32,839
to ask for that.

118
00:05:33,279 --> 00:05:33,879
An answer?

119
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:34,839
Alright.

120
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:36,959
We will post
all the investigation results

121
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:38,000
online,

122
00:05:38,360 --> 00:05:41,319
including how you and
your boyfriend staged

123
00:05:41,519 --> 00:05:43,480
the entire camera installation
in the guest room.

124
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:46,839
It was her!

125
00:05:47,079 --> 00:05:48,360
She told me to install the camera
in the room

126
00:05:48,639 --> 00:05:49,319
to smear the resort!

127
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:50,600
She made me do it!

128
00:05:50,759 --> 00:05:52,399
Are you crazy?
What are you talking about?

129
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:55,920
It is too late to deny it now.

130
00:05:57,319 --> 00:05:58,959
The public will see the truth.

131
00:06:00,399 --> 00:06:02,879
Tomorrow's headline will be

132
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:05,360
"Story of a Fake Anti-Scam Influencer".

133
00:06:09,319 --> 00:06:09,879
I...

134
00:06:10,839 --> 00:06:12,920
I just wanted to get more views.

135
00:06:13,959 --> 00:06:15,319
I didn't mean to blow it up this big.

136
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:18,800
You can leave now.

137
00:06:25,959 --> 00:06:26,800
Now,

138
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:29,959
let us talk about compensation.

139
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:31,480
Compensation?

140
00:06:31,839 --> 00:06:32,279
Of course.

141
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:34,519
After everything happened at the resort,

142
00:06:34,839 --> 00:06:36,360
including my employee's medical expenses

143
00:06:36,519 --> 00:06:37,560
and compensation for emotional distress,

144
00:06:38,319 --> 00:06:39,240
that will be expensive.

145
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:41,040
Fine. I will pay.

146
00:06:41,279 --> 00:06:42,279
How much? I will pay it all.

147
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:43,720
That depends on

148
00:06:44,519 --> 00:06:45,839
how much the person who hired you

149
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:47,240
paid you.

150
00:06:48,519 --> 00:06:49,120
No one.

151
00:06:50,519 --> 00:06:51,439
No one hired me.

152
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:53,879
Since you refuse to cooperate,

153
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:55,560
let's meet in court.

154
00:06:59,040 --> 00:07:00,240
I don't know who he is.

155
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:02,160
He only told me

156
00:07:02,639 --> 00:07:04,560
to do my best to
ruin the resort's reputation.

157
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:07,519
He told me to do whatever it takes
to destroy the resort's reputation,

158
00:07:08,079 --> 00:07:09,560
so that you'll lose all your customers.

159
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:10,839
After this,

160
00:07:11,279 --> 00:07:12,279
I could get one million.

161
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:16,079
(He Jinchen is really careful.)

162
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:19,720
This is everything I know.

163
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:21,079
Please,

164
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:23,160
I beg you, don't expose me.

165
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:25,199
I make my living online.

166
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:27,040
Miss Lin,

167
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:29,680
never describe yourself as
a journalist again.

168
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:30,800
You don't deserve it.

169
00:07:31,319 --> 00:07:32,759
And don't treat the kind people online

170
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:33,600
like fools.

171
00:07:38,639 --> 00:07:40,120
Regarding the camera incident
a week ago,

172
00:07:40,399 --> 00:07:42,319
we have cooperated with the police
to get to the bottom of it.

173
00:07:42,839 --> 00:07:44,360
The influencer staged the whole thing

174
00:07:44,759 --> 00:07:46,279
for personal gains

175
00:07:46,439 --> 00:07:47,240
and to smear us.

176
00:07:47,639 --> 00:07:49,319
The staff member who
helped install the camera

177
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:50,879
is in a relationship with the influencer

178
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:51,800
and has been fired.

179
00:07:52,160 --> 00:07:54,040
All guest rooms have been inspected

180
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:56,160
and no hidden devices were found.

181
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:58,319
We welcome continued oversight
from our guests.

182
00:07:59,120 --> 00:07:59,759
Hereby,

183
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:02,279
for any management failures,

184
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:05,160
I sincerely apologize
on behalf of Gu Corporation Resort.

185
00:08:06,279 --> 00:08:06,839
At the same time,

186
00:08:07,439 --> 00:08:08,199
we will pursue

187
00:08:08,279 --> 00:08:10,360
legal action against the spread of
false information online.

188
00:08:11,199 --> 00:08:12,959
We also thank everyone

189
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:14,959
for the continued support of our resort.

190
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:25,000
It has been dragging on for so long.

191
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:27,759
What's taking so long
with the resort acquisition?

192
00:08:28,439 --> 00:08:28,879
Dad,

193
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:31,160
everything was going smoothly,

194
00:08:31,560 --> 00:08:33,799
except for one small issue that came up.

195
00:08:34,399 --> 00:08:36,480
I want a result, not excuses.

196
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:38,679
You must secure the resort
as soon as possible.

197
00:08:41,039 --> 00:08:41,480
Dad,

198
00:08:42,559 --> 00:08:44,840
the resort is in the spotlight now.

199
00:08:45,159 --> 00:08:46,159
Everyone is watching.

200
00:08:46,720 --> 00:08:48,120
If we make any big moves,

201
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:49,440
people will use it against us.

202
00:08:50,440 --> 00:08:51,799
We should wait.

203
00:08:51,960 --> 00:08:52,679
Wait?

204
00:08:53,159 --> 00:08:55,600
Can Meiyan afford to
wait in its current state?

205
00:08:58,879 --> 00:08:59,600
Forget it.

206
00:09:00,159 --> 00:09:01,320
You are too indecisive.

207
00:09:01,759 --> 00:09:02,759
Stay out of this.

208
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:04,039
That's it.

209
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:07,480
Yes.

210
00:09:19,679 --> 00:09:20,159
Madam,

211
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:21,960
the master sent me to take you home.

212
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:41,600
Let go!

213
00:09:42,039 --> 00:09:43,080
I cannot breathe!

214
00:09:43,279 --> 00:09:44,360
Let go!

215
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:49,320
This uniform

216
00:09:49,399 --> 00:09:51,039
makes you the most handsome

217
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:52,399
staff member in our resort.

218
00:09:53,639 --> 00:09:54,639
Are you making fun of me?

219
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:57,480
All this acting has worn me out.

220
00:09:58,320 --> 00:10:00,399
The He family is full of cunning people.

221
00:10:00,639 --> 00:10:01,879
If your performance isn't convincing,

222
00:10:02,279 --> 00:10:03,279
they're not going to buy it.

223
00:10:19,840 --> 00:10:20,799
(Shaoze.)

224
00:10:22,320 --> 00:10:23,279
(Enjoyed the drink?)

225
00:10:24,399 --> 00:10:24,879
(You...)

226
00:10:28,799 --> 00:10:29,919
(Trying to drug me?)

227
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:32,080
(You are still too green.)

228
00:10:34,679 --> 00:10:35,279
(Wait!)

229
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:38,639
(Uncle Mu.)

230
00:10:38,799 --> 00:10:39,559
(My father is not here.)

231
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:41,120
(On the raw material issue,)

232
00:10:41,399 --> 00:10:42,279
(you can discuss it with me.)

233
00:10:42,759 --> 00:10:44,879
(To cut costs and boost effectiveness,)

234
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:46,639
(you used raw materials)

235
00:10:46,759 --> 00:10:48,360
(containing carcinogens
in the cosmetics.)

236
00:10:49,759 --> 00:10:50,840
(This is just a clip.)

237
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:54,360
(If we get engaged,)

238
00:10:54,720 --> 00:10:55,720
(I'll give you the whole thing.)

239
00:10:57,200 --> 00:10:58,399
(He Jinchen is your brother.)

240
00:10:59,320 --> 00:11:00,120
(Would you betray him?)

241
00:11:02,039 --> 00:11:03,720
(Does he still care about siblinghood?)

242
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:05,840
(If it were not for his own gain,)

243
00:11:06,039 --> 00:11:07,360
(why would he have kicked Jinchuan out?)

244
00:11:08,519 --> 00:11:09,120
(So)

245
00:11:09,799 --> 00:11:11,720
(I want my own interests too.)

246
00:11:12,720 --> 00:11:13,080
(Fine.)

247
00:11:14,120 --> 00:11:14,840
(Deal.)

248
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:16,679
(But)

249
00:11:17,679 --> 00:11:18,919
(you must keep your word.)

250
00:11:48,240 --> 00:11:49,159
Turns out

251
00:11:49,279 --> 00:11:50,759
we played our parts pretty well.

252
00:11:57,960 --> 00:11:59,480
Beautiful lady,

253
00:12:00,120 --> 00:12:01,960
how may I help you?

254
00:12:09,399 --> 00:12:11,559
I need a hug to refresh myself.

255
00:12:11,679 --> 00:12:13,000
I'm so tired.

256
00:12:16,360 --> 00:12:17,240
Tell me,

257
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:20,679
since He Jinchen failed this time,

258
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,679
will he come up with another scheme?

259
00:12:22,919 --> 00:12:23,519
Don't worry.

260
00:12:24,039 --> 00:12:24,639
He Jinchen

261
00:12:24,799 --> 00:12:25,519
has been focused

262
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:27,120
on Meiyan International's
internal affairs.

263
00:12:28,200 --> 00:12:29,279
The people we planted

264
00:12:29,519 --> 00:12:30,679
were all removed by him.

265
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:34,440
We have lost all our people?

266
00:12:36,440 --> 00:12:38,080
But we have a new pawn now.

267
00:12:39,080 --> 00:12:40,200
We don't yet know

268
00:12:40,399 --> 00:12:41,600
how effective

269
00:12:41,919 --> 00:12:42,600
this pawn will be.

270
00:12:48,580 --> 00:12:50,780
(He Jinxi)

271
00:12:54,799 --> 00:12:55,200
Hello?

272
00:12:55,879 --> 00:12:57,759
Shaoze, where are you?

273
00:13:01,240 --> 00:13:01,879
I'm busy.

274
00:13:03,720 --> 00:13:05,600
We need to try on
the engagement gowns tomorrow.

275
00:13:05,879 --> 00:13:06,840
I hope you can come with me.

276
00:13:10,960 --> 00:13:11,639
Alright.

277
00:13:13,480 --> 00:13:14,279
See you tomorrow.

278
00:13:14,679 --> 00:13:14,960
Bye.

279
00:13:15,159 --> 00:13:15,559
Bye.

280
00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:20,440
You're still her fiancé.

281
00:13:20,960 --> 00:13:22,159
You'd better go home and prepare.

282
00:13:22,360 --> 00:13:23,519
Tomorrow will be busy.

283
00:13:23,879 --> 00:13:24,639
It's fake.

284
00:13:26,279 --> 00:13:28,480
But you still have to
play your part well.

285
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:36,080
We are the real ones.

286
00:14:05,660 --> 00:14:07,240
♪Time stole♪

287
00:14:07,240 --> 00:14:10,360
(Elegant)
♪the proof of our love♪

288
00:14:10,420 --> 00:14:15,260
♪Hidden in the moonlight,
lost in the clouds♪

289
00:14:15,260 --> 00:14:19,820
♪Tangled glances and love fall together♪

290
00:14:19,820 --> 00:14:24,740
♪Into a spiral of thoughts,
memories rewinding♪

291
00:14:24,740 --> 00:14:28,540
♪Feelings both strange and familiar♪

292
00:14:28,540 --> 00:14:33,340
♪I just know you're
where my heart belongs♪

293
00:14:33,340 --> 00:14:36,180
♪Can't remember
when this flutter started♪

294
00:14:36,180 --> 00:14:38,860
♪Or how it's supposed to end♪

295
00:14:39,220 --> 00:14:44,780
♪Goodbye to the world rushing in♪

296
00:14:45,180 --> 00:14:51,980
♪Let me hide in your eyes
and never leave♪

297
00:14:52,260 --> 00:14:56,940
♪Feel the rhythm of your heartbeat♪

298
00:14:57,100 --> 00:15:03,900
♪Every tomorrow seems worth the wait♪

299
00:15:04,220 --> 00:15:11,020
♪Let me fill the emptiness of a century♪

300
00:15:11,220 --> 00:15:15,700
♪As the wind brushes past your hem♪

301
00:15:15,700 --> 00:15:19,060
♪All my hidden feelings come undone♪

302
00:15:19,060 --> 00:15:25,980
♪Right as I confess my love♪
